Class BoardCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • clueGame.BoardCell

  • public class BoardCell
extends java.lang.Object

    BoardCell

    This class stores the location of a cell, the type of space it is, and whether or not the cell has a door attached.
    Since:
    2017-10-09
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Adam Nelson, Nathaniel Fuller, Youjun Lee
